    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban smoking & vaping during working hours",
        "additional_details": "We believe the ban could also help people become fitter and healthier. We believe it may also save companies, the NHS and the Government money, and result in more time working and less time not working. We also believe it may lead to more people actually giving up smoking and vaping.",
        "background": "We urge the Government to pass a law which bans people from smoking and vaping during working hours. We believe this would be better for the environment and allow more work to get done.",
